    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty\u2014it\u2019s basically a dream on wheels! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel and feel how smooth it is. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
