    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 engineering. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, both recently serviced to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency and throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits flawless paint depth while the interior remains free of bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and cosmetically immaculate, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of the analog driving experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
